race.comment: GRAND CHIEF (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with eight wins and 10 minors from 24 tries. Missed the frame latest (20.10) when sixth over 342m at this track in a Best 8 race Best 8. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. PAW EVA (1) is a last start placegetter in Grade 5 company, jumping from this box and finishing a 1.75 lengths third over 300m at Murray Bridge. Has a very honest record from this same draw, including a win and six minors. Rates a leading chance. BREAKER OF RULES (5) missed the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 400m at Gawler in 22.80. Has the ability and can find winning form again. AIR CRUISER (7) jumps at a shorter journey and still warrants respect.
